  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to proof the safety and efficacy of the new ICD sytem
      (Iforia/Ilesto). The devices are available with DF-1 and DF4 connection. A special focus is
      set on the ICD system with DF4 connection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
